hh3cStorageMIB.name: hh3cStorageMIB
hh3cStorageMIB.contactinfo: Platform Team H3C Technologies Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China Http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085
hh3cStorageMIB.description: This MIB describes the general information of storage device, such as the property, configuration and management.

hh3cRaidCapability.name: hh3cRaidCapability
hh3cRaidCapability.description: This object identifies if the agent support raid management.

hh3cFcCapability.name: hh3cFcCapability
hh3cFcCapability.description: This object identifies if the agent support FC(fiber channel) management.

hh3cNasCapability.name: hh3cNasCapability
hh3cNasCapability.description: This object identifies if the agent support NAS(Network Attached Storage).

hh3cAdaptiveRepCapability.name: hh3cAdaptiveRepCapability
hh3cAdaptiveRepCapability.description: This object identifies if the agent support adaptive replication. With adaptive replication option, data from the primary resource is continuously replicated to a replication resource unless the system determines it is not practical or possible, such as when there is insufficient bandwidth. For continuous replication to occur, a continuous replication resource is used to stage the data being replicated from the primary resource. Similar to a cache, as soon as data comes into the continuous replication resource, it is written to the replication resource.

hh3cRemoteRepCapability.name: hh3cRemoteRepCapability
hh3cRemoteRepCapability.description: This object identifies if the agent support remote replication.

hh3cSafeCacheCapability.name: hh3cSafeCacheCapability
hh3cSafeCacheCapability.description: This object identifies if the agent support safe cache.

hh3cSyncMirrorCapability.name: hh3cSyncMirrorCapability
hh3cSyncMirrorCapability.description: This object identifies if the agent support synchronized mirror.

hh3cAsyncMirrorCapability.name: hh3cAsyncMirrorCapability
hh3cAsyncMirrorCapability.description: This object identifies if the agent support asynchronous mirror.

hh3cTimeMarkCapability.name: hh3cTimeMarkCapability
hh3cTimeMarkCapability.description: This object identifies if the agent support time mark.

hh3cSseCapability.name: hh3cSseCapability
hh3cSseCapability.description: This object identifies if the agent support SSE(Storage Service Enable).

hh3ciSCSITargetEnable.name: hh3ciSCSITargetEnable
hh3ciSCSITargetEnable.description: This object identifies if the agent support iSCSI target.

hh3cFcTargetEnable.name: hh3cFcTargetEnable
hh3cFcTargetEnable.description: This object identifies if the agent support FC target.

hh3cServerLocationLedState.name: hh3cServerLocationLedState
hh3cServerLocationLedState.description: This object identifies the state of storage device's location led.

hh3cServerResetButtonState.name: hh3cServerResetButtonState
hh3cServerResetButtonState.description: This object identifies if the reset button is enable.

hh3cServerPowerButtonState.name: hh3cServerPowerButtonState
hh3cServerPowerButtonState.description: This object identifies if the power button is enable.

hh3cServerPowerState.name: hh3cServerPowerState
hh3cServerPowerState.description: This object identifies the state of power supply in the server, and is valid when UPS has been configured successful. The value 'online' means power supply is well-balanced. The value 'onlinebypass' means supply power without ups. The value 'onbattery' means supply power with battery. The value 'unknown' means the power supply state is unknown.

hh3cDeuTable.name: hh3cDeuTable
hh3cDeuTable.description: This table contains some information of a particular DEU(Disk Enclosure Unit).

hh3cDeuEntry.name: hh3cDeuEntry
hh3cDeuEntry.description: An entry containing management information applicable to a particular DEU.

hh3cDeuIndex.name: hh3cDeuIndex
hh3cDeuIndex.description: This object identifies the index of hh3cDeuTable. The DEU identified by a particular value of this index is the same object as identified by the same value of entPhysicalIndex.

hh3cDeuIDLed.name: hh3cDeuIDLed
hh3cDeuIDLed.description: This object identifies the state of storage DEU's led.

hh3cDeuDiskScan.name: hh3cDeuDiskScan
hh3cDeuDiskScan.description: The operation of scanning the table. When the value of this object is set to 'action', the operation of disk scanning is touched off.

hh3cStorageInterfaceTable.name: hh3cStorageInterfaceTable
hh3cStorageInterfaceTable.description: This table describes the interface information of the network.

hh3cStorageInterfaceEntry.name: hh3cStorageInterfaceEntry
hh3cStorageInterfaceEntry.description: An entry containing management information applicable to a particular interface.

hh3cStorageInterfaceIndex.name: hh3cStorageInterfaceIndex
hh3cStorageInterfaceIndex.description: This object identifies the index of Hh3cStorageInterfaceEntry. The interface identified by this index is the same interface as identified by the same value of ifIndex.

hh3cStorageInterfaceGateway.name: hh3cStorageInterfaceGateway
hh3cStorageInterfaceGateway.description: This object identifies the gateway address of interface.

hh3cStorageInterfaceGatewayType.name: hh3cStorageInterfaceGatewayType
hh3cStorageInterfaceGatewayType.description: This object identifies the gateway address type of interface.

hh3cStorageInterfaceMTU.name: hh3cStorageInterfaceMTU
hh3cStorageInterfaceMTU.description: This object identifies the MTU of interface.

hh3cBondingTable.name: hh3cBondingTable
hh3cBondingTable.description: This table describes the information of the Bonding interface.

hh3cBondingEntry.name: hh3cBondingEntry
hh3cBondingEntry.description: An entry containing management information applicable to a particular Bonding interface.

hh3cBondingIndex.name: hh3cBondingIndex
hh3cBondingIndex.description: This object identifies the index of hh3cBondingEntry. The interface identified by this index is the same interface as identified by the same value of ifIndex.

hh3cBondingPortList.name: hh3cBondingPortList
hh3cBondingPortList.description: An entry contains management information applicable to a particular bonding interface. Every two bytes describe the ifIndex of an interface, and an interface belongs to one bonding group only. An interface should be deleted from the portlist of the bonding group it belongs to before it is added to another bonding group.

hh3cScsiAdapterTable.name: hh3cScsiAdapterTable
hh3cScsiAdapterTable.description: This table containing some information of the SCSI(Small Computer System interface) adapter.

hh3cScsiAdapterEntry.name: hh3cScsiAdapterEntry
hh3cScsiAdapterEntry.description: An entry containing management information applicable to a particular SCSI adapter.

hh3cAdapterNumber.name: hh3cAdapterNumber
hh3cAdapterNumber.description: This object identifies the index of the adapter .

hh3cAdapterDesc.name: hh3cAdapterDesc
hh3cAdapterDesc.description: This object describes some information of the adapter.

hh3cAdapterType.name: hh3cAdapterType
hh3cAdapterType.description: This object identifies the type of adapter. If the value of this object is not equal to 'fc', the associated object(such as hh3cFcAdapterMode, hh3cFcAdapterIWWPNs,hh3cFcAdapterTWWPNs,hh3cFcAdapterPortState,hh3cFcAdapterModeSwitch) will be invalid.

hh3cFcAdapterMode.name: hh3cFcAdapterMode
hh3cFcAdapterMode.description: This object identifies the mode type of adapter.

hh3cFcAdapterInitiatorWwpnName.name: hh3cFcAdapterInitiatorWwpnName
hh3cFcAdapterInitiatorWwpnName.description: This object describes the FC's adapter WWPN(World Wide Port Name) numbers.

hh3cFcAdapterTargetWwpnName.name: hh3cFcAdapterTargetWwpnName
hh3cFcAdapterTargetWwpnName.description: This object describes the FC's target WWPN numbers.

hh3cFcAdapterPortState.name: hh3cFcAdapterPortState
hh3cFcAdapterPortState.description: This object identifies the state of adapter's interface.

hh3cFcAdapterModeSwitch.name: hh3cFcAdapterModeSwitch
hh3cFcAdapterModeSwitch.description: This object identifies if the adapter work on a target mode.

hh3cExtVoltageTable.name: hh3cExtVoltageTable
hh3cExtVoltageTable.description: This table contains some entity extend information of the voltage.

hh3cExtVoltageEntry.name: hh3cExtVoltageEntry
hh3cExtVoltageEntry.description: An entry containing management information applicable to the voltage.

hh3cExtVoltagePhysicalIndex.name: hh3cExtVoltagePhysicalIndex
hh3cExtVoltagePhysicalIndex.description: This object identifies the entity index of voltage.

hh3cExtVoltagePhysicalName.name: hh3cExtVoltagePhysicalName
hh3cExtVoltagePhysicalName.description: This object identifies the entity name of voltage.

hh3cExtVoltageLowThreshold.name: hh3cExtVoltageLowThreshold
hh3cExtVoltageLowThreshold.description: The low-threshold for the voltage. When voltage is lower than low-threshold, a notification will be sent.

hh3cExtVoltageHighThreshold.name: hh3cExtVoltageHighThreshold
hh3cExtVoltageHighThreshold.description: The high-threshold for the voltage. When voltage is higher than high-threshold, a notification will be sent.

hh3cExtCriticalVoltageLowThreshold.name: hh3cExtCriticalVoltageLowThreshold
hh3cExtCriticalVoltageLowThreshold.description: The critical low threshold for voltage. If the voltage is lower too much than the entity needs, the entity will halt.

hh3cExtCriticalVoltageHighThreshold.name: hh3cExtCriticalVoltageHighThreshold
hh3cExtCriticalVoltageHighThreshold.description: The critical high threshold for voltage. If the voltage is higher too much than the entity needs, the entity will halt.

hh3cExtShutdownVoltageLowThreshold.name: hh3cExtShutdownVoltageLowThreshold
hh3cExtShutdownVoltageLowThreshold.description: The voltage is lower than the critical low threshold. If the voltage is lower too much than the entity needs, the entity halts now.

hh3cExtShutdownVoltageHighThreshold.name: hh3cExtShutdownVoltageHighThreshold
hh3cExtShutdownVoltageHighThreshold.description: The voltage is higher than the critical high threshold. If the voltage is higher too much than the entity needs, the entity halts now.

hh3cSoftwareInfoString.name: hh3cSoftwareInfoString
hh3cSoftwareInfoString.description: This object identifies if the software's information.

hh3cStorCriticalLowerTemperatureThreshol.name: hh3cStorCriticalLowerTemperatureThresholdNotification
hh3cStorCriticalLowerTemperatureThreshol.description: The hh3cStorCriticalLowerTemperatureThresholdNotification indicates the temperature is lower than the threshold. If the temperature is lower too much than the entity needs, the entity will halt.

hh3cStorTemperatureTooLow.name: hh3cStorTemperatureTooLow
hh3cStorTemperatureTooLow.description: The hh3cStorTemperatureTooLow indicates the temperature is lower than the threshold. If the temperature is lower too much than the entity needs, the entity halts now.

hh3cExtVoltageLowThresholdNotification.name: hh3cExtVoltageLowThresholdNotification
hh3cExtVoltageLowThresholdNotification.description: The hh3cExtVoltageLowThresholdNotification indicates the Voltage is lower than the low-threshold.

hh3cExtVoltageHighThresholdNotification.name: hh3cExtVoltageHighThresholdNotification
hh3cExtVoltageHighThresholdNotification.description: The hh3cExtVoltageHighThresholdNotification indicates the Voltage is lower than the high-threshold.

hh3cExtCriticalVoltageLowThresholdNotifi.name: hh3cExtCriticalVoltageLowThresholdNotification
hh3cExtCriticalVoltageLowThresholdNotifi.description: The hh3cExtCriticalVoltageLowThresholdNotification indicates the Voltage is lower than the critical low threshold.

hh3cExtCriticalVoltageHighThresholdNotif.name: hh3cExtCriticalVoltageHighThresholdNotification
hh3cExtCriticalVoltageHighThresholdNotif.description: The hh3cExtCriticalVoltageHighThresholdNotification indicates the Voltage is higher than the critical high threshold.

hh3cExtVoltageTooLow.name: hh3cExtVoltageTooLow
hh3cExtVoltageTooLow.description: The hh3cExtVoltageTooLowNotification indicates the Voltage is lower than the critical low threshold, and the entity halt now!

hh3cExtVoltageTooHigh.name: hh3cExtVoltageTooHigh
hh3cExtVoltageTooHigh.description: The hh3cExtVoltageTooHighNotification indicates the Voltage is higher than the critical high threshold, and the entity halt now!

hh3cExtBatteryStateNotification.name: hh3cExtBatteryStateNotification
hh3cExtBatteryStateNotification.description: The hh3cExtBatteryStateNotification indicates the raid battery entity's state changes.

hh3cDiskIOErrorNotification.name: hh3cDiskIOErrorNotification
hh3cDiskIOErrorNotification.description: The hh3cDiskIOErrorNotification indicates that a disk occurred I/O error.

hh3cRaidCreateNotification.name: hh3cRaidCreateNotification
hh3cRaidCreateNotification.description: The hh3cRaidCreateNotification indicates that a array is created.

hh3cRaidDeleteNotification.name: hh3cRaidDeleteNotification
hh3cRaidDeleteNotification.description: The hh3cRaidDeleteStateNotification indicates that a array is deleted.

hh3cRaidHideStateNotification.name: hh3cRaidHideStateNotification
hh3cRaidHideStateNotification.description: The hh3cRaidFailedNotification indicates that a array hide or unhide.

hh3cRaidRunStateNotification.name: hh3cRaidRunStateNotification
hh3cRaidRunStateNotification.description: The hh3cRaidDegradeNotification indicates that a array state change.

hh3cRaidImportNotification.name: hh3cRaidImportNotification
hh3cRaidImportNotification.description: The hh3cRaidFailedNotification indicates that a thrid array is imported.

hh3cRaidRebuildStartNotification.name: hh3cRaidRebuildStartNotification
hh3cRaidRebuildStartNotification.description: The hh3cRaidRebuildStartNotification indicates that a array start to rebuild.

hh3cRaidRebuildFinishNotification.name: hh3cRaidRebuildFinishNotification
hh3cRaidRebuildFinishNotification.description: The hh3cRaidRebuildStartNotification indicates that a array fininsh rebuild.

hh3cRaidRebuildPauseNotification.name: hh3cRaidRebuildPauseNotification
hh3cRaidRebuildPauseNotification.description: The hh3cRaidRebuildPauseNotification indicates that pause a array rebuilding.

hh3cRaidRebuildInterruptNotification.name: hh3cRaidRebuildInterruptNotification
hh3cRaidRebuildInterruptNotification.description: The hh3cRaidRebuildInterruptNotification indicates that interrupt a array rebuilding.

hh3cSoftwareModuleFailNotification.name: hh3cSoftwareModuleFailNotification
hh3cSoftwareModuleFailNotification.description: The hh3cSoftwareModuleFailNotification indicates that software module(s) fail.

hh3cRaidBatteryExpiredNotification.name: hh3cRaidBatteryExpiredNotification
hh3cRaidBatteryExpiredNotification.description: The hh3cRaidBatteryExpiredNotification indicates RAID Battery lifetime had expired.

hh3cRaidBatteryWillExpireNotification.name: hh3cRaidBatteryWillExpireNotification
hh3cRaidBatteryWillExpireNotification.description: The hh3cRaidBatteryWillExpireNotification indicates RAID Battery lifetime will expire.

hh3cLvOnlineFailNotification.name: hh3cLvOnlineFailNotification
hh3cLvOnlineFailNotification.description: The hh3cLvOnlineFailNotification indicates lv(s) on vd fail to online.

hh3cLvOfflineFailNotification.name: hh3cLvOfflineFailNotification
hh3cLvOfflineFailNotification.description: The hh3cLvOfflineFailNotification indicates lv(s) on vd fail to offline.

hh3cRaidRunNotification.name: hh3cRaidRunNotification
hh3cRaidRunNotification.description: The hh3cRaidRunNotification indicates that a array is running.

hh3cExtVoltageNormal.name: hh3cExtVoltageNormal
hh3cExtVoltageNormal.description: The hh3cStorVoltageRecoveryNotification indicates the Voltage has recovered in reference.

hh3cDiskPowerOnNotification.name: hh3cDiskPowerOnNotification
hh3cDiskPowerOnNotification.description: The hh3cDiskPowerOnNotification indicates that a disk is power on.

hh3cDiskPowerOffNotification.name: hh3cDiskPowerOffNotification
hh3cDiskPowerOffNotification.description: The hh3cDiskPowerOffNotification indicates that a disk is power off.
